WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.119 --> 00:00:02.419
This is what a parent or athlete sees when

2
00:00:02.419 --> 00:00:03.899
they book with you.

3
00:00:03.899 --> 00:00:06.059
They land on your personal page,

4
00:00:06.059 --> 00:00:11.319
yourname.lessonspot.app. No app to download,

5
00:00:11.319 --> 00:00:13.319
no account to create.

6
00:00:13.319 --> 00:00:15.519
Returning families just type their email,

7
00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:17.520
and we pull up their info.

8
00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:19.779
New ones fill out a quick form.

9
00:00:19.779 --> 00:00:22.100
From there, they pick the lesson type,

10
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:24.119
thirty minutes, an hour,

11
00:00:24.119 --> 00:00:27.879
hitting, pitching, group, whatever you offer at the price

12
00:00:27.879 --> 00:00:29.079
you set.

13
00:00:29.079 --> 00:00:31.879
Then they grab times that actually work.

14
00:00:31.879 --> 00:00:35.299
The calendar only shows the openings you've made available,

15
00:00:35.299 --> 00:00:37.559
and if they're booking for more than one kid,

16
00:00:37.559 --> 00:00:40.860
they can assign each session to the right athlete.

17
00:00:40.860 --> 00:00:43.319
They review everything grouped by name,

18
00:00:43.319 --> 00:00:46.139
confirm, and they're locked in.

19
00:00:46.139 --> 00:00:49.020
After that, customers can look up their bookings,

20
00:00:49.020 --> 00:00:52.020
reschedule, or cancel right from your page.

21
00:00:52.020 --> 00:00:54.919
No more texting back and forth at midnight.

22
00:00:54.919 --> 00:00:58.000
Built-in reminder emails go out five days and two

23
00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.680
days before every lesson,

24
00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:01.520
so no one forgets.

25
00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:04.319
This is the experience that wins parents over the

26
00:01:04.319 --> 00:01:05.379
first time they book
